title: No Smoking/No loud music.
posting_body: ['Duplex locate near Atlantic Blvd and Whitter Blvd in East LA.', '800 sqft.', "Technically, it's a 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, with a LARGE utility room which easily could be use as extra bedroom/office!!", 'Garage storage space available.', 'Max of 4 occupants.', 'Newly remodeled Kitchens, high floor ceiling with nice open floor plans, Street Parking, Hookups is ready for Stackable Washer/Dryer Combo Unit in the back.', 'No Smoking/No loud music.', 'The owner pays for water, trash.', 'Renter pays for electricity and gas.', 'Requirements (for each adult over 18 years old):', '1) Rental Application', '2)Two Months Paystubs', '3)Two Months Bank Statements', '4)Credit Reports *Credit Score 670 or above*', "5)Copies of ID's", '6)Copies of Social Security Cards', '7)Income must be 2.5 Times Rent', '8)Must Sign Addendum to certifies financial health, liquidity and Income.']
